// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1734 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 145e5095-646c-5d5b-83f6-2991335e2480

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*")
